Alembic migrations for xavfsizmi-api.

Run from apps/api/:
  uv run alembic upgrade head      # apply all
  uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"
  uv run alembic downgrade -1      # roll back one step

Migrations are applied automatically by the API container's entrypoint in production;
in local dev run `uv run alembic upgrade head` once after `docker compose up -d`.
